Package it.polimi.se2019.view.gui

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BoardPane
    GUI controller of the board pane displayed in main game screen
    BoardSquare
    GUI controller of the content of a board tile, contained in board pane
    GraphicUpdateHandler
    GUI update handler
    GraphicView
    View interface override for GUI
    GuiResourcePaths
    Final class used to store all various resource paths used in GUI
    GuiUtils
    Static class to provide common GUI methods used in all GUI controllers
    LoginScreen
    GUI login screen, starting scene of the GUI application
    Main
    Main class of GUI
    MainScreen
    GUI controller of the main game scene, interact with all sub-controllers of the scene to handle game interactions and display correct data on the screen
    OtherPlayerPane
    GUI controller of player panes of opponent players of the one owning this GUI view
    PlayerPane
    GUI controller of main player pane, namely the owner of this view
